  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate a safe threshold for when to remove chest tubes in
      patients based on the amount of drainage present.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Measurement of pleural fluid drainage in chest tubes of trauma patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
